headline: Stocks Set to Open Higher as Investors Await Key U.S. Economic Data
summary: December S&P 500 E-Mini futures (ESZ25) are up +0.19%, and December Nasdaq 100 E-Mini futures (NQZ25) are up +0.39% this morning as investors gear up for a week of key U.S. economic data amid growing expectations for a Federal Reserve interest rate cut next month.

headline: EU approves €450m Czech support for onsemi’s new SiC chip facility
